OL,3,CConsumer confidence plunges among
OL,4,Cyounger adults
OL,6,FConsumer confidence has plunged among
OL,7,Ftraditionally optimistic younger
OL,8,Fadults amid fears for their personal
OL,9,Ffinances and the wider economy,
OL,10,Ffigures show.
OL,12,FGfK's long-running Consumer Confidence
OL,13,FIndex remained unchanged at an overall
OL,14,Fscore of minus 23 in June.
OL,16,FHowever, the analyst said this was was
OL,17,F"misleading as, beneath the surface,
OL,18,Fthere are new signs that confidence is
OL,19,Fweakening".
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@JO]
