OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781830076
OL,3,CConsumer confidence plunges among
OL,4,Cyounger adults
OL,6,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,7,Fdirector at GfK, said: "The biggest
OL,8,Ffall this month is among those aged 16
OL,9,Fto 29, traditionally one of the most
OL,10,Foptimistic groups.
OL,12,F"Here confidence has dropped 11 points
OL,13,Fover the past month to minus two, the
OL,14,Flowest level seen for two years,
OL,15,Fdriven by large falls in views on both
OL,16,Ftheir own personal finances and the
OL,17,Fwider economy.
OL,26,@oD@XOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781830076
OL,3,CConsumer confidence plunges among
OL,4,Cyounger adults
OL,6,F"More broadly, there are now no
OL,7,Fdemographic groups with a positive
OL,8,Fconfidence score, including higher-
OL,9,Fincome households earning #50,000 or
OL,10,Fmore, who have slipped back into
OL,11,Fnegative territory as of June.
OL,13,F"Confidence remains subdued and
OL,14,Fvulnerable to further economic or
OL,15,Fpolitical uncertainty."
OL,17,FOverall, confidence in personal
OL,18,Ffinances over the coming year remained
OL,19,Fflat at minus two, four points lower
OL,20,Fthan this time last year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781830076
OL,3,CConsumer confidence plunges among
OL,4,Cyounger adults
OL,6,FThe measures of both personal finances
OL,7,Fand the economy over the previous 12
OL,8,Fmonths were both slightly down, by two
OL,9,Fpoints and three points respectively,
OL,10,F"reflecting the sense that things have
OL,11,Fbeen extremely tough over the last
OL,12,Fyear for so many", GfK said.
OL,14,FThe only measure to increase was
OL,15,Fexpectations for the wider economy
OL,16,Fover the next 12 months, up two points
OL,17,Fto minus 36 but still eight points
OL,18,Fbelow this time last year.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@QO]
