OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781830076
OL,3,CConsumer confidence plunges among
OL,4,Cyounger adults
OL,6,FThe major purchase index, an indicator
OL,7,Fof confidence in buying big ticket
OL,8,Fitems, remained at minus 20, four
OL,9,Fpoints lower than June last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
